column5: Hit the river early morning before work on Saturday. Only had a little over an hour to play and this fresh hen made my day!
Nice fsh, what did it hit?
very nice.  congrats on the fish.  also love the solitude thats surround around you.
Laz VS Miss chrome  winner: Laz
i used to dream of doing something like that when i drove past rivers to work
better insert that pic in the progression thread Laz...she is a beauty for sure  nice shootin
Very nice bar of chrome Laz
After I left Fidel (Highdrifter) tactfully connected with this Male on the Fly Rod!  Nicely Done Buddy.
WOW  One day I wish to catch something of that size and magnitude.
Fatty! Both fish are nice.   TDunn
